WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.769 --> 00:00:14.179
Architecture is Legos.

00:00:14.179 --> 00:00:19.160
Its houses on the street, big buildings in
the city.

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:20.400
Its design.

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:24.520
Its your dream and the guidance counselor
said math is important.

00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:29.210
Architecture tells stories and It looks like
music.

00:00:29.210 --> 00:00:31.520
Its got so many styles.

00:00:31.520 --> 00:00:34.700
Its your major and its not sleeping a lot.

00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:39.640
You told your parents its starting to feel
like the words written on a locker.

00:00:39.640 --> 00:00:40.640
Architorture.

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:41.640
Its subjective.

00:00:41.640 --> 00:00:42.910
Its a broken will.

00:00:42.910 --> 00:00:44.900
Its thrilling.

00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:49.450
Sometimes it looks like what it means and
sometimes it looks like crumpled paper.

00:00:49.450 --> 00:00:51.360
Its metaphor and simile.

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:53.640
It is ornate and brutal.

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:55.170
Its habitable art.

00:00:55.170 --> 00:00:56.610
Its invention.

00:00:56.610 --> 00:00:58.430
Its inspiration.

00:00:58.430 --> 00:01:01.110
Its mathematics and physics.

00:01:01.110 --> 00:01:05.100
Its functional and aesthetically pleasing
or not.

00:01:05.100 --> 00:01:11.930
It is simplified and complex, clear and opaque,
abstract because it can be.

00:01:11.930 --> 00:01:13.550
Its a duck.

00:01:13.550 --> 00:01:15.340
It is symmetrical and perfect.

00:01:15.340 --> 00:01:18.650
It is asymmetrical like you.

00:01:18.650 --> 00:01:21.040
It is proportions and rules.

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:25.270
It is form follows function or function follows
form.

00:01:25.270 --> 00:01:28.219
Its your new lens for looking at the world.

00:01:28.219 --> 00:01:29.880
Its the Fountainhead.

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:35.640
Its a small paycheck and a long road to the
word you cant use in your title.

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:41.340
Its selling yourself to self-absorbed people
and selling your soul to self-absorption.

00:01:41.340 --> 00:01:46.049
Its your boss in a publication one week and
getting sued the next.

00:01:46.049 --> 00:01:51.270
Its running an office and keeping everyone
busy - running out of work and letting people

00:01:51.270 --> 00:01:52.270
go.

00:01:52.270 --> 00:01:54.750
Its under promising and overachieving.

00:01:54.750 --> 00:01:59.619
Its problem solving, drawing, drafting, sketching,
model making and changes.

00:01:59.619 --> 00:02:03.880
It is construction documents and CYA.

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:09.450
Its setbacks, codes, zoning laws, structural,
mechanical, electrical, and AV.

00:02:09.450 --> 00:02:12.330
Its plans, sections, elevations, and details.

00:02:12.330 --> 00:02:19.810
It is coordinating every word and every drawing
with every player.

00:02:19.810 --> 00:02:21.040
Its not about design.

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:25.050
Its about 3 expensive letters.

00:02:25.050 --> 00:02:26.530
Its your kids dream.

00:02:26.530 --> 00:02:30.850
Its the translation of an idea like Van Goghs
starry night.

00:02:30.850 --> 00:02:32.860
Its technology and tools.

00:02:32.860 --> 00:02:35.680
Edifying, seductive and clean.

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:41.560
It is the greatest profession in the world
and the worst business.

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:43.230
Its dinner party conversation.

00:02:43.230 --> 00:02:45.160
Its absurd and perfect.

00:02:45.160 --> 00:02:48.200
Its wishing you were a banker.

00:02:48.200 --> 00:02:50.760
Its what you always wanted to be.

00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:52.160
Its a myth.

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:53.860
Its your passion.

00:02:53.860 --> 00:02:55.950
Its here then its gone.

00:02:55.950 --> 00:02:57.200
Like you.

00:02:57.200 --> 00:02:58.000
Dust.

